Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, January 6 (XINHUA) -- General Liu Huaqing, 
vice-chairman of the Chinese Central Military Commission (CMC), 
and his party left here this morning for an official goodwill 
visit to Thailand and Indonesia. 
  Liu and his party have been invited by the supreme commander 
of the Thai armed forces, Air Chief Marshal Woranat Aphichari, 
