Director of the General Office of the Chinese Communist Party 
Central Committee Hu guangbao, Vice-Foreign Minister Tang 
Jiaxuan, Director of the General Office of CMC Cheng Jianning, 
as well as embassy officials of the relevant countries. 
  Liu's party includes Liu's wife Xu Hongxia, Deputy Chief of 
the General Staff of the PLA Xu Huizi and some other PLA leaders. 

