<H3> <TI>   Ren Jianxin Pays Visit to Indonesia, Singapore </TI></H3>
<H4>   Sees Chief Justice, Attorney General </H4>
<F P=102> OW0501120894 Beijing XINHUA in English 1152 GMT 5 Jan 94 </F>
