<H3> <TI>   Hebei Radio Station Extends Newscast </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK0701064794 Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 6 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK0701064794 </F>
<F P=104>  Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Summary] Beginning on 10 January, the Hebei Provincial 
People's Broadcasting Station will extend its newscast from the 
present 20 minutes to 30 minutes. The first newscast will still 
take place at 0700 [Beijing standard time] to 0730 every morning 
and the newscast will be repeated from 0800 to 0830 every 
morning. The contents of the newscast will change somewhat with 
the addition of new columns. 

</TEXT>

