<F P=100> Northeast Asia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Liaoning Secretary Addresses Forum on Press Work </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK0501042494 Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK0501042494 </F>
<F P=104>  Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Responsible comrades of the press units directly 
under the province and the press units of the central 
authorities stationed in the province were invited to the 
conference room of the standing committee of the provincial 
party committee on 4 January to attend a forum on press work 
held by the provincial party committee and government. Gu 
Jinchi, secretary of the provincial party committee, chaired the 
forum. Responsible comrades of LIAONING RIBAO, the Liaoning 
Provincial Radio and Television Department, the Liaoning 
People's Broadcasting Station, the Liaoning Television Station, 
and the Liaoning Branch of XINHUA News Agency gave speeches. 
They reviewed the achievements and problems of the press units 
of the province and those of the central authorities stationed 
in the province in their efforts to persistently take economic 
construction as the central task and adhere to correct press 
guidance in 1993. They also offered views and suggestions on 
ways to make this year's press and propaganda work successful. 
  Vice Governor Zhang Rongmao spoke to put forward specific 
requirements on how press units should strengthen guidance 
through positive examples and improve the propaganda front. He 
urged press units under party leadership to adhere to the 
principle of propaganda through positive example, correctly 
report the provincial situation, and guide the people throughout 
the province to make contributions to accelerating Liaoning's 
economic construction. 
  Gu Jinchi, secretary of the provincial party committee, also 
spoke after attentively listening to the speeches. He said: In 
1993, press units of the province persistently took the 
guidelines of the 14th party congress as guidance and economic 
construction as the central task and carried out a great amount 
of work focusing on the arrangements of the provincial party 
committee and government, thus promoting Liaoning's economic and 
other work. The year 1994 will be one when the largest number 
of China's major reform measures will be executed and also a 
crucial year for the endeavor to more rapidly establish the 
socialist market economy system. Therefore, it is very 
important to do a good job in news reports. 
  He emphasized: The focus of the 1994 press work should be on 
conscientious implementation of the guidelines of the 14th party 
congress, especially those of the third plenary session of the 
14th party Central Committee, and the execution of major reform 
measures should be regarded as an important part of news reports 
to facilitate the establishment of the socialist market economy 
system. Press units should intensify publicity of economic work, 
adhere to the essential criterion of development, and emphasize 
improvement of economic efficiency as the focus to bring about 
healthy, sustained, and rapid development in Liaoning's economy. 
In publicizing the spiritual civilization, they should adhere 
to the major trends to encourage people's enthusiasm for 
building socialism and for plunging themselves into economic 
construction. They should do a good job in publicizing unity 
and stability to provide a good social environment for reform 
and opening up and to ensure the development of economic 
construction and other undertakings. 
  Gu Jinchi also put forward specific demands for improvement 
of the leading bodies and contingents of the press units of the 
province. 

</TEXT>

